<p>I have a list int int like this:</p>  <pre><code>let x = [[2; 3; 4]; [4; 5]; [2; 3]] </code></pre>  <p>and an int for example 1. I want to add this int on the first list and return result like this: </p>  <pre><code>[[1; 2; 3; 4]; [4; 5]; [2; 3]] </code></pre>  <p>What is the most convenient way to do this?</p>